responsibility for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>policy on sexual orientation and transgender equality</li>\n  <li>cross-government equality strategy and legislation</li>\n</ul>\n\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2017-07-12T11:12:19Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Minister for Equalities","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/minister-for-women-and-equalities","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state--48","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state--48","base_path":"/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state--48","content_id":"9162d9f4-f99e-4cfd-95dc-2eb5a7181e79","details":{"body":"<p>MOJ responsibilities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>family justice and mediation (including Cafcass)</li>\n  <li>female offenders</li>\n  <li>mental health</li>\n  <li>mental capacity (including Office of the Public Guardian)</li>\n  <li>criminal offences gateway</li>\n  <li>coroners, burials, cremation and inquiries policy</li>\n  <li>equalities</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Women and Equalities responsibilities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>women and the economy, including women on boards and reducing the gender pay gap</li>\n  <li>challenging cultural stereotypes</li>\n  <li>stopping violence against women and girls</li>\n  <li>domestic, international and EU commitments on equality including the Equality and Human Rights Commission (EHRC)</li>\n  <li>supporting the Secretary of State on lesbian, gay, bisexual, and transgender (LGBT) policy</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2017-07-12T11:22:23Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Minister for Women","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state--48","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state--64","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state--64","base_path":"/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state--64","content_id":"e7318005-9858-438d-b377-86d621383cc1","details":{"body":"<p>The minister’s responsibilities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>women’s equality (including addressing the gender pay gap and getting more women on company boards)</li>\n  <li>lesbian, gay, bisexual, and transgender policy</li>\n  <li>the Equality and Human Rights Commission (including the equality legal framework and international commitments)</li>\n  <li>dealing with bullying in schools (including homophobic bullying)</li>\n  <li>early years and childcare (including the government’s commitment of 30 hours free childcare per week)</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2016-08-08T17:56:31Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Parliamentary Under Secretary of State for Women, Equalities and Early Years","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state--64","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/minister-for-women","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/minister-for-women","base_path":"/government/ministers/minister-for-women","content_id":"8472bc5e-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Minister for Women has overall responsibility for policy on gender equality.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2020-02-17T16:28:52Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State (Minister for Women)","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/minist